{"tid":538200,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街了 馬雲狙擊騰訊 聽日700玩完","createTime":"2018-01-23T12:05:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-23T15:46:27.000Z","uid":74425,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"19281c56937b817a6e790f8e2b11ace0e40db0fd","tid":538200,"uid":74425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/789874787871258/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F789874787871258%2F&d=gtlVt1sD%2B290nI6en9BbUkkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=48bedc22\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/789874787871258/</a><br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴主席馬雲稱，對於小學生沉迷騰訊旗下王牌手遊『王者榮耀』，自己作為父母都覺得不高興，認為當局要有措施限制。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲曾揚言「餓死也不做遊戲」，他強調不是因為眼紅騰訊，至作出批評。<br />\n<br />\n但阿里巴巴最終逐步擴大遊戲業務版圖，成立遊戲事業部門。<br />\n<br />\n馬雲強調做遊戲並非為錢，而是要為老人設計有意思的遊戲，以及為教育、孩子成長及文化有關的遊戲。<br />\n<br />\n他坦言阿里巴巴現在還沒有這個能力，但就正是構思當中。<br />\n<br />\n中共好快做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75ed94795f874f6989f7add18fd92faf613de6d","tid":538200,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"有人嬲嬲豬 在美國cap水唔夠人多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0404b6df5701f2a789f7080e2c8462c65ca91ac1","tid":538200,"uid":34869,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b75ed94795f874f6989f7add18fd92faf613de6d","tid":538200,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:23:31.000Z","msg":"有人嬲嬲豬 在美國cap水唔夠人多呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-23T12:24:26.000Z","msg":"響美國點cap到水<img src=